features: Start an instant collection of original and licensed Matchbox cars and trucks with this 20-pack.
These 1:64 scale cars and trucks feature realistic details and authentic designs to inspire kid-driven adventure rooted in realism.​​
Keep the entire set or hand them out as party favors or individual prizes to budding car enthusiasts and collectors.​​
These realistic vehicles celebrate the cars and trucks that keep the world moving.
This 20-pack makes a great gift for Matchbox collectors and kids 3 years old and older, who love creative push-around play.
body.description: Roll out an instant collection with this 20-pack of Matchbox cars and trucks. The perfect gift for kids or collectors, it features a wide variety of colors, silhouettes and licenses of 1:64 scale Matchbox vehicles with highly realistic details, authentic decos and real, rolling wheels. Whether they're cruising through the city, racing to the rescue or driving full throttle toward adventure, these cars will deliver hours of imaginative play. Includes a variety of 20 Matchbox vehicles. Not for use with some Matchbox sets. Colors and decorations may vary.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great collection of Matchbox cars and trucks
reviews.reviewText: Gave it for Christmas gift for my grand daughter age 4 1/2 and she loved it. Beautiful midget cars and trucks.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 23, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Ordered these and they shipped so quickly! Great value too!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 17, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Ordered this for my boys for their Christmas gift. We got a terrific selection of cars, including fun vehicles like an ATV, a trailer, a trash truck, an army truck, am earth movers, etc. in addition to typical cars and trucks. They are going to love this assortment! :)

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 6, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I love matchbox cars. I will always buy these cars before any other set. They always have pretty cute cars in there sets. Always well made. My favorite cat toy.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 9, 2024
reviews.reviewText: PROS: No Duplicates, Each car in retail packageCONS: Shipping Label on Retail BoxUnlike the Hot Wheel box, Matchbox did not have any duplicates at all. This was a gift for my grandson. Unfortunately, this item was not shipped in a brown box. As you would have guessed, shipping label right on the retail box. I had to gift bag the cars and be creative to make it exciting for him to see what was in the bag.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 9, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars No Duplicates - So Happy
reviews.reviewText: After buying multiple hot wheels boxes with constant duplicates, bought my first Matchbox 50 Pack and got 50 different vehicles. Absolutely no duplicates, which is really wonderful. Considering both are made by Mattel, why don't the Hot Wheels 50 and 60 packs be duplicate free also. Has a mixed ranged of old school cars from the 40s - 70s etc and modern cars 2000s and beyond.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 10, 2023
reviews.reviewText: My 3-year old grandson loved the gift and the variety of cars (the cupcake car and the taco truck were VERY well-received!), and he can organize and re-arrange them to his heart's content. Great gift, solid value for the price!

reviews.reviewerName: Buena figura, el cambio de color cuando le da el sol es total
reviews.reviewText: Excelente vienen los vehículos marcandos en la caja, son de tarjeta corta, la caja se ve chica pero vienen los 50 vehículos anunciados en el set

La realidad es que no vienen ninguno de los autos que están en la imagen, pero la caja trae muy buenos carritos, especialmente los autos y las camionetas.Digo, si eres fan de los autos de construcción o servicios de emergencia seguro será un plus.
You can never go wrong choosing these as a gift for a little boy. My grandaughters enjoy playing with them as well. These are great quality well made cars and you get a really nice selection of them.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United Kingdom on February 3, 2024
reviews.reviewText: A good assortment from the 2022 range. There is no indication on the page to say what year the 50 pack comes from. I took a chance hoping it might be the 2024 range, as that is the year in which I ordered it. I'm not too dissapointed though that it was a much older pack. If Amazon would show year of manufacture, or more details from the box, that would help.
